# ==========================

**/node_modules/
**/bower_components/
**/jspm_packages/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/target/
**/out/
.npm/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

